            "title": "招商轮船称公司没有船舶在波斯湾 油轮运价大涨",
            "image": "https://inews.gtimg.com/news_ls/OE6FzobgoCyLkdnnYaxAsXB3G_GfsubGqd5dlu7d0dnjUAA_870492/0",
            "link": "https://new.qq.com/rain/a/20260325A0403N00",
            "author": "连续阅读180天",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-25 12:44:12",
            "description": "<div class=\"rich_media_content\"><section>【<span dt-eid=\"\" dt-params=\"\"><span class=\"qnt-link\"><span class=\"qnt-link-text\">招商轮船</span></span></span>称公司没有船舶在波斯湾 <span dt-eid=\"\" dt-params=\"\"><span class=\"qnt-link\"><span class=\"qnt-link-text\">油轮运价</span></span></span>大涨】财联社3月25日电，招商轮船证券部人士今日透露，目前公司没有船舶滞留波斯湾，战争后也没有通过风险区域的计划，而是走其他运输航线，目前油轮运价比战争前上涨超50%。</section></div>",
